        ResultSet rs = null;    // Declare 'rs' variable and set its data type to "ResultSet". (Add the above two lines)  Initialize resultset. If not successful, print corresponding message at end of method execution or by using a Try-catch block as follows: ((try {...} catch(SQLException se))).
